<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login - ElectroStore</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header', { user: user, cart: cart }) %>

    <main class="main-content">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="card" style="max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h2 class="card-title">
                        <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Login to ElectroStore
                    </h2>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card-body">
                    <% if (error) { %>
                        <div class="alert alert-error">
                            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> <%= error %>
                        </div>
                    <% } %>
                    
                    <form action="/login" method="POST">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="username" class="form-label">
                                <i class="fas fa-user"></i> Username
                            </label>
                            <input 
                                type="text" 
                                id="username" 
                                name="username" 
                                class="form-control" 
                                placeholder="Enter your username"
                                required
                            >
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="password" class="form-label">
                                <i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Password
                            </label>
                            <input 
                                type="password" 
                                id="password" 
                                name="password" 
                                class="form-control" 
                                placeholder="Enter your password"
                                required
                            >
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">
                                <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Login
                            </button>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <p>Don't have an account? <a href="/signup">Sign up here</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <div class="security-warning">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                        <strong>Demo Credentials:</strong> 
                        <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
                            <li><strong>Admin:</strong> username: <code>admin</code>, password: <code>admin</code></li>
                            <li><strong>Regular User:</strong> Create your own account via Sign Up</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card mt-3" style="max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h3 class="card-title">
                        <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> Lab Instructions
                    </h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4>How to practice Blind XSS:</h4>
                    <ol>
                        <li><strong>Create a regular user account</strong> (or use admin credentials above)</li>
                        <li><strong>Browse products</strong> and add items to your cart</li>
                        <li><strong>Checkout</strong> and enter shipping address</li>
                        <li><strong>Inject XSS payload</strong> in the "Delivery Notes" field</li>
                        <li><strong>Wait for admin bot</strong> to view your order (runs every 60 seconds)</li>
                        <li><strong>Monitor your payload execution</strong> (e.g., using a request bin)</li>
                    </ol>
                    
                    <div class="xss-warning mt-2">
                        <h4>
                            <i class="fas fa-bug"></i> XSS Vulnerability Location
                        </h4>
                        <p>The admin order details page renders delivery notes using <code><%- %></code> (unescaped output) instead of <code><%= %></code> (escaped output).</p>
                        <p><strong>Sample payload:</strong> <code><!-- <script>alert('XSS')</script> --></code></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>